anonymousMaximumLimitChecks.en-CA: Create an account to participate in more checks.

authenticatedMaximumLimitChecks.en-CA: Leave or delete a check to participate in other checks.

deleteAccountHint.en-CA: This will delete your account and any checks that don't contain other users. Checks containing other users will grant ownership to any other valid user. This action cannot be reversed.

emailAddProvider.en-CA: Sign in to add {provider} as an authentication provider for your account.

inviteAsEditorHint.en-CA: New users can make changes to this check

inviteAsEditorSettingsHint.en-CA: Newly created checks will invite users with the ability to make changes to the check

inviteAsViewerHint.en-CA: New users can only view this check

inviteAsViewerSettingsHint.en-CA: Newly created checks will invite users with the ability to view the check

linkPaymentsHint.en-CA: Select a contributor's balance to link your payment account

linkPaymentsAnonymousHint.en-CA: Sign in to link your payment account

linkPaymentsSwitchHint.en-CA: Your account will be unlinked from {previousContributor}

newChecksRequireAnInviteHintChecked.en-CA: Newly created checks will require users to be invited before they can access the check

newChecksRequireAnInviteHintUnchecked.en-CA: Newly created checks will allow any user with a link to access the check

openDescription.en-CA: Anyone on the internet can access this check

passwordHint.en-CA: Your new password must be at least 8 characters long and should not be used in other places.

paymentAccountHiddenHint.en-CA: Users will not see your payment account

paymentAccountSettingsHint.en-CA: Users in checks that you're participating in will be instructed to send money to your {walletType} account

paymentAccountUnsetHint.en-CA: No payment account set up by {user}

providerAddProvider.en-CA: {email} already uses {existingProvider} as an authentication provider. Sign in to add {newProvider} as an authentication provider for your account.

reauthenticateHint.en-CA: To keep your account safe, you must re-validate your credentials to change that setting. Your settings have not been updated yet.

regenerateInviteWarning.en-CA: The current invitation link will no longer work

restrictedDescription.en-CA: Only users invited with the link below can access this check

trackTicket.en-CA: You can track the progress of ticket #{ticketNumber} here.
